  "workspaceId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "dataSourceInstructions": "Gold_consume Instructions\r\n\r\nFrequently Bought Together / Recommendations\r\n\r\n- Resolve the product anchor using product_id or a case-insensitive\r\n  lookup on Bronze_Ingest.products.name.\r\n\r\nPrimary Source:\r\n- Use Gold_consume.fact_product_affinity_topk for recommendations.\r\n\r\nFallback:\r\n- If Top‑K has no rows for the anchor, use fact_product_affinity with:\r\n    • pair_cnt ≥ 5 noise filter\r\n    • limit to Top‑10 based on ranking\r\n\r\nRanking:\r\n- Order results by:\r\n    1) lift DESC\r\n    2) confidence_lhs_to_rhs DESC\r\n    3) pair_cnt DESC\r\n\r\nQuality Thresholds:\r\n- Prefer recommendations where:\r\n    • lift ≥ 1.5\r\n    • confidence_lhs_to_rhs ≥ 0.15\r\n  If none meet thresholds, return best available and state limited evidence.\r\n\r\nProduct Name Resolution:\r\n- Join rhs_item_id to Bronze_Ingest.products for human-readable names.\r\n\r\nEdge Handling:\r\n- If no associations exist: return\r\n  “Not enough historical data for this product yet.”",
  "displayName": "Gold_Consume",
  "type": "lakehouse_tables",
  "userDescription": "Gold_consume.fact_product_affinity_topk\r\nPurpose: Precomputed Top‑K “frequently bought together” associations for fast recommendations.\r\nColumns:\r\n\r\nlhs_item_id STRING\r\nrhs_item_id STRING\r\npair_cnt BIGINT\r\nsupport_lhs DOUBLE\r\nsupport_rhs DOUBLE\r\nsupport_pair DOUBLE\r\nconfidence_lhs_to_rhs DOUBLE\r\nlift DOUBLE\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nGold_consume.fact_product_affinity\r\nPurpose: Full association table (used as fallback when Top‑K has no coverage).\r\nColumns:\r\n\r\nlhs_item_id STRING\r\nrhs_item_id STRING\r\npair_cnt BIGINT\r\nsupport_lhs DOUBLE\r\nsupport_rhs DOUBLE\r\nsupport_pair DOUBLE\r\nconfidence_lhs_to_rhs DOUBLE\r\nlift DOUBLE",
